description:
Superman must battle Kalibak and Darkseid on Apokolips--but his mind has been switched with Jimmy Olsen's, leaving him in the wrong body!

This is a job for... Jimmy Olsen?
name: Jimmy Olsen versus Darkseid

description:
Lobo brings Bizarro to Earth to stir up trouble for Superman. And when the backwards baddy searches for a bride-to-be, Lois gets caught up in the action.

A Bizarro Love Story! (Also Guest-Starring Lobo)
name: Bride of Bizarro

description:
Returning from a mission in space, Superman is shocked to learn that he's been missing for over a year. Even more shocking is when his biological parents and a group of Kryptonians arrive on Earth!

Jonathan and Martha Kent...dead?
name: Family Reunion: Part One

description:
Meet Clark Kent: Public Enemy Number One! Is there another culprit responsible for his actions? If Clark doesn't find out, Metropolis's new Most Wanted may be in for another new career--making license plates!

Clark Kent - Metropolis' Most Wanted!
name: Clark Kent: Public Enemy

description: A re-publishing of the second issue of the adult comic with sketches, behind the scenes info, etc.

The biggest hit horror series of the year returns with an all-new seven-issue series written by David (Stray Bullets) Lapham! Adeline Pratt is a survivor. She is holding together what is left of her family while they are under constant siege. But as she has to face off against family members who have turned Crossed, can she bring herself to stay calm and in control? Or are the pressures of this horrific new World just too much for anyone to bare? What is the price of surviving in this new World, could it be that the only way to persevere is to be even more evil than the Crossed are? Imagine, for a moment, the worst crimes against humanity. Picture the cruelest affronts to decency. Conjure your darkest nightmares... and then realize it could all be so much worse. When civilization crumbles in one terrifying moment; when people are gleefully breaking into unthinkable acts of violence all around you; when everyone you love has died screaming in agony: What do you do? There is no help. There is no hope. There is no escape. There are only the Crossed.

Hero Tales we will be transported in ancient China and its centuries-old legends. It is said that there are seven heroes connected to the seven stars of Ursa Major and two of them are destined to struggle for dominance of Earth. One of these is enclosed inside the young Taito, a guy who still does not know the enormous power that has. But the sudden attack by a strange man will forever change his life and force him to get on the road to retrieve a stolen something precious to him. Thus begins her adventure that takes him through the huge China!
name: Vol. 1
